<div class="container">
  <div class="row front-header">
    <div class="content">
      <h1><%= config.title %></h1>
      <p>
          Hello! 👋 I’m Filip and I’m a software gardener. 🌺 I write and nurture good code, best practices, and maintainable software. Mostly working with JavaScript. (Specifically, the React ecosystem.)
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <h2>🛠 Projects</h2>
    <p>I run my own consulting gig, but really I mostly work at <a href="https://spicefactory.co/" target="_blank">SpiceFactory.</a> We’re hacking away at various projects, solving problems, and making our clients happy. If you want to learn more about the commercial stuff I’ve worked on, <a href="/about">have a look here.</a> Or read up on what I’m doing <a href="/open-source-software">in open source land.</a> </p>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h2>🏫 Video Courses</h2>
    <p>✨ In September 2018, I published the course <a href="https://www.packtpub.com/web-development/hands-web-development-react-video" target="_blank">Hands on Web Development with React.</a> It’s aimed at newcomers and I explain in great length what exactly it covers <a href="/2018/hands-on-web-development-with-react-course">in this blog post.</a></p>
    <p>I’m working an another one that’s set to be published in December 2018. So stay tuned!</p>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h2>💬 Speaking</h2>
    <p>I like to speak at conferences and meetups. Sharing knowledge and meetings new people is exciting! Interested in having me speak at your event? <a href="/speaking">Read more about my past experience.</a></p>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h2>✍️ Writing</h2>
    <% page.posts.limit(5).each(function(post){ %>
      <div class="post-card">
        <p class="date-info"><%= date(post.date, config.date_format) %></p>
        <p>
          <a href="<%- url_for(post.path) %>">
            <%= post.title %>
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    <% }) %>
    <p class="text-small"><a href="/writing" title="All essays">See all essays.</a></p>
  </div>
</div>

<%- partial('navigation-footer') %>
